🔹 Hive Support in Spark
Explanation

“Hive support in Apache Hive allows Spark to interact with Hive tables, use HiveQL, and access the Hive metastore for structured data processing.”

Code
spark = SparkSession.builder \
    .appName("HiveExample") \
    .enableHiveSupport() \
    .getOrCreate()

spark.sql("SHOW TABLES").show()

